---
layout: layout.njk
title: Proof
metaTitle: "Career Coaching Proof and Case Studies | Askia"
metaDescription: "An anonymized proof library showing how Askia helps professionals improve positioning, interviews, and compensation outcomes."
breadcrumbs:
  - name: "Home"
    url: "/"
  - name: "Resources"
    url: "/resources/"
  - name: "Proof"
    url: "/proof/"
---
<div class="resource-theme-page">
<section class="section resource-theme-hero">
  <div class="container hero-grid">
    <div class="hero-copy">
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">Proof Library</p>
      <h1 class="hero-title section-title-glow">Proof that goes beyond generic promises</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Real examples of how Askia sharpens positioning, interviews, and offer outcomes.</p>
      <p class="hero-support">This library exists to show how search strategy, materials, interviews, and compensation work together in actual career moves.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-card">
      <strong>What you’ll see</strong>
      <ul>
        <li>Anonymized career case studies</li>
        <li>What changed in the positioning</li>
        <li>The result and the lesson behind it</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</div>

<section class="section section-tight">
  <div class="container two-col-grid">
    <div class="content-panel">
      <h2 class="section-title section-title-glow">Why this matters</h2>
      <p>Career coaching pages are easy to promise on. Proof pages are where the useful detail starts: what was broken, what changed, and what outcome followed.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="content-panel">
      <h2 class="section-title section-title-glow">Why Askia is credible here</h2>
      <p>{{ expertCredibility.founder.shortBio }}</p>
      <ul class="checklist">
        {% for item in expertCredibility.founder.metrics %}
        <li>{{ item }}</li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="pillar-header">
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">Cases</p>
      <h2 class="section-title section-title-glow">Proof by role, market, and service</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="resources-grid">
      {% for item in caseStudies.items %}
      <a class="resource-card resource-card-link" href="/proof/{{ item.slug }}/">
        <h3>{{ item.title }}</h3>
        <p>{{ item.summary }}</p>
        <span>{{ item.outcome }}</span>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
